name: experiment
label: Experiment
help: Each experiment is a simulation of the climate system under specific hypothesis. Consult the Overview or the Documentation section to learn more about these experiments.

name: variable
label: Variable
help: This is a subset of all available CMIP5 variables. Consult the Overview or the Documentation section to learn more about these variables.

labels.maximum_2m_temperature_in_the_last_24_ho: Maximum 2m temperature in the last 24 hours
labels.minimum_2m_temperature_in_the_last_24_ho: Minimum 2m temperature in the last 24 hours

name: model
label: Model
help: This is a subset of all available CMIP5 models. Consult the Documentation section to learn more about these variables.

name: ensemble_member
label: Ensemble member
help: The main member is usually the member denoted r1i1p1. Other members are simulations which were obtained using slightly different initial conditions, dates or model parameters. Consult the Overview or the Documentation section to learn more about ensemble members.

name: period
label: Period
help: These are the calendar periods for which daily data are available.  Periods are formatted as "yyyymmdd-yyyymmdd", that is, start and final date of the period, where "yyyy", "mm" and "dd" stand for year, month and day, respectively.
